(54, 'Hanayo', '5f4dcc3b5aa765d61d8327deb882cf99', 'Hanayo', 'Rice Goddess', 'Koizumi', '1999-01-17', '2018-06-16 05:28:28', 'hanayokoizumi@gmail.com', 'http://love-live.wikia.com/wiki/Hanayo_Koizumi', 'Otonikizaka Gakuen', 1, 1, 'upload/Hanayo-Koizumi-love-live-school-idol-project-37513197-363-500.jpg', 'Hanayo is a very shy, quiet character who doesn\'t normally voice her opinions. She is very reserved and will often let other people make decisions for her because of this. Hanayo is also easily scared. However, her personality changes when it comes to school idols, as she is very enthusiastic about them.\r\n\r\nHanayo loves to eat anything, especially rice balls. For that reason, she usually gets upset with her weight, as shown in Season 2 Episode 7.', 1, 2, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2018-07-07 11:34:10', 5),
