(69, 'Mikuru', '5f4dcc3b5aa765d61d8327deb882cf99', 'Mikuru', '', 'Natsuki', '2000-07-07', '2018-06-21 15:47:24', 'natsukimikuru@gmail.com', 'http://aikatsu.wikia.com/wiki/Mikuru_Natsuki', 'Natsuki Greening Garden ', 1, 1, 'upload/tumblr_o2ud0hV9Hs1tcnj7co1_1280.jpg', 'Mikuru is a sweet girl who is very energetic and well-meaning. She is very bright and loves flowers, to the point where she frequently compares them with other things. She also has a talent with clothing. She is rather free-spirited and casts her miracle, Mikuru\'s Miracle, upon stage and in everyday life. Due to her expertise with flowers, she likes to compare everything with them.', 1, 2, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2018-06-25 10:11:15', 3);
